moves.name: Absorb
moves.battle_effect: The user attacks by draining targets of their nutrients. The user's HP will be restored by a portion of the damage dealt.
moves.secondary_effect: User recovers half the damage inflicted.

moves.name: Accelerock
moves.battle_effect: The user smashes into the target at high speed. This move always goes first.

moves.name: Acid
moves.battle_effect: Opposing Pok√©mon are attacked with a spray of harsh acid. This may also lower their Sp. Def stats.
moves.secondary_effect: May lower opponent's Special Defense one stage.

moves.name: Acid Armor
moves.battle_effect: The user boosts its Defense stat for a while by altering its cellular structure to become liquefied.

moves.name: Acid Spray
moves.battle_effect: The user attacks by spitting fluid that works to melt the target. This also harshly lowers the target's Sp. Def stat.
moves.secondary_effect: Lowers opponent's Special Defense two stages.

moves.name: Acrobatics
moves.battle_effect: The user nimbly strikes the target. This attack does massive damage if the user isn't holding an item.
moves.secondary_effect: Increases damage by 100% if user is not holding an item.

moves.name: Acupressure
moves.battle_effect: The user applies pressure to stress points, sharply boosting one of its or its allies' stats.
moves.secondary_effect: Raises one of the user's stats randomly by two stages.

moves.name: Aerial Ace
moves.battle_effect: The user attacks by confounding targets with swift movements before slashing.

moves.name: Aeroblast
moves.battle_effect: A vortex of air is shot at the target to inflict damage. This move has a heightened chance of landing a critical hit.
moves.secondary_effect: Has an increased Critical Hit ratio
